{"tha-ap54:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap54:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap54:0.3":"2 Sataramsittheraapadana ","tha-ap54:1.1":"“Ubbiddham selamaruyha, ","tha-ap54:1.2":"nisidi purisuttamo; ","tha-ap54:1.3":"Pabbatassaviduramhi, ","tha-ap54:1.4":"brahmano mantaparagu. ","tha-ap54:2.1":"Upavittham mahaviram, ","tha-ap54:2.2":"devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap54:2.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap54:2.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap54:3.1":"‘Esa buddho mahaviro, ","tha-ap54:3.2":"varadhammappakasako; ","tha-ap54:3.3":"Jalati aggikhandhova, ","tha-ap54:3.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhato. ","tha-ap54:4.1":"Mahasamuddovakkhubbho, ","tha-ap54:4.2":"annavova duruttaro; ","tha-ap54:4.3":"Migarajavasambhito, ","tha-ap54:4.4":"dhammam deseti cakkhuma’. ","tha-ap54:5.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap54:5.2":"padumuttaranayako; ","tha-ap54:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap54:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap54:6.1":"‘Yenayam anjali dinno, ","tha-ap54:6.2":"buddhasettho ca thomito; ","tha-ap54:6.3":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap54:6.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap54:7.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap54:7.2":"angirasasanamako; ","tha-ap54:7.3":"Vivattacchado sambuddho, ","tha-ap54:7.4":"uppajjissati tavade. ","tha-ap54:8.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap54:8.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap54:8.3":"Sataramsiti namena, ","tha-ap54:8.4":"araha so bhavissati’. ","tha-ap54:9.1":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap54:9.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap54:9.3":"Sataramsimhi namena, ","tha-ap54:9.4":"pabha niddhavate mama. ","tha-ap54:10.1":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","tha-ap54:10.2":"jhayi jhanarato aham; ","tha-ap54:10.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap54:10.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap54:11.1":"Satthikappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap54:11.2":"caturo ramanamaka; ","tha-ap54:11.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap54:11.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap54:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap54:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap54:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap54:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sataramsi thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap54:14.1":"Sataramsittherassapadanam dutiyam. "}